{{Notability|date=March 2015}}

'''LINGO''' is a [[mathematics|mathematical]] [[modeling language]] designed for formulating and solving [[Program optimization|optimization]] problems, including [[linear programming|linear]], [[integer programming|integer]], and [[nonlinear programming]] problems.<ref>http://www.lindo.com/</ref>

